Calibrates elevation of KER SuperDARN radar (creates correct elev.normal)
Tested under Lubuntu 20.04

Requirements: RSTLite (or RST) library
	      libz
	      gcc

INSTALL:

1)Install RSTlite (or RST) from https://github.com/SuperDARN/rst

2)Link include and lib directories from RST distribution to home directory

3)call:
 make all


USAGE:
./recalc_elevation_DAVIT_linear  inputfilename outputfilename


